longBusinessSummary: Fram Skandinavien AB (publ) provides digital consultancy and professional services in Vietnam. The company offers software as a service, web application, mobile application, and eCommerce development services; and system performance optimization and DevOps managed services. It also provides digital managed services; and invests in digital consumer, blockchain, and other technology domains. Fram Skandinavien AB (publ) was founded in 1893 and is based in Uppsala, Sweden.
